name: Steampunk Bullet Train (Canceled)
blurb: Spark Plug Games presents Steampunk Bullet Train: our very first crowd-funded video game!

rewards.reward: $5? Awesome! Your name will be mentioned in the thank you section of the credits and you\u2019ll receive a Bronze Flight Wings Logo icon in our forums. Oh, and did we mention that everyone who donates gets a copy of the game? Hey guess what, everyone who donates via Kickstarter gets a copy of SBT!

$10...you clearly like us twice as much as the people giving $5! You'll receive a special digital letter signed by the team thanking you for your support, thank you in the credits, and a Silver Flight Wings Logo icon in our forums

For showing us three times as much love as those $5 donators, you'll receive a schematics digital poster of the SteamPunk Bullet Train, the special digital letter, the even more special thank you in the credits, and the most special prize of all: Gold Flight Wings Logo icon in our forums.
Wow! $25 - you rock! You'll receive the official game poster for SteamPunk Bullet Train (mailed just to you!), all of the above, and even a Platinum Flight Wings Logo icon in our forums!

This ain't no small chunk of change - thanks for believing in us! You'll receive the official t-shirt for SteamPunk Bullet Train, all of the aforementioned rewards, and a One-Star Platinum Flight Wings Logo icon in our forums.

If you give us $75, we're going to give you some bling in return! You'll receive a logo pendant in the shape of the Bullet Train Flight Wings, all of the rewards above, and a very shiny Two-Star Platinum Flight Wings Logo in our forums.

My friend, for your love - we will give you some hand-crafted love in return. You'll receive a 3D printed, hand-painted model of the Interceptor (from the game!), have an enemy pilot named after you, receive all of the above AND get an Interceptor Logo icon in our forums.

What goes around comes around - for $250, we'll give you some super fun stuffs! You'll receive a 3D printed, hand-painted model of the Track Tank (from the game!), have an enemy pilot named after you, receive all of the above (excluding the Interceptor model) AND get a Track Tank Logo icon in our forums.

Very nice! For $500 (there can only be three of you!) you'll receive a 3D printed, hand-painted model of the Rat Rod Bullet Train from the game, have a boss pilot named after you (like a boss), receive all of the above (excluding the Interceptor and Track Tank models) AND get Rat Rod Bullet Train Logo icon in our forums.

Wow wow wee waa!  For a whopping $1000 of game developer love, you will be included in weekly development meetings (via phone/Skype), be IMMORTALIZED as a character to choose from at the beginning of the game, receive all of the above (one choice of model!) AND receive a ridiculously shiny Three-Star Platinum Flight Wings Logo icon in our forums.
